<h1>Photo#878222</h1>
</div>
<div><div id='zzq49n27vn6jl1pPhotoDetailView79' class='CPhotoDetailView-view CPhotoDetailView'> <div class='river-photo'>
<a href="/content/Photo/detail/photoid/878222/size/big/">
<img class='river-photo' src="/photos/archive/medium/878222.jpg">
