<h2>Rapid Descriptions</h2>
<div><div id='zzq49n27vn6jl1pRiverRapidView39' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid101426">Anticipation</a></b> (Class IV, Mile 0.7)<br>
<p>Step-down slide with a small drop at the bottom.</p><br>
<br clear=right>
</div><div id='zzq49n27vn6jl1pRiverRapidView40' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid101428">Painted Gauge</a></b> (Class N/A, Mile 0.9)<br>
<p>See the description of runnable levels in the Main tab.</p><br>
<br clear=right>
</div><div id='zzq49n27vn6jl1pRiverRapidView41' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid101425">Staircase Falls</a></b> (Class 5.3, Mile 1.0)<br>
<p>See the description on the main page. The left side is unrunnable; right of the island is way gnarly.</p><br>
<br clear=right>
</div><div id='zzq49n27vn6jl1pRiverRapidView42' class='CRiverRapidView-view CRiverRapidView'> <b><a name="rapid101427">Brian's Cannon</a></b> (Class IV+, Mile 1.5)<br>
<p>Two large slides back-to-back, with a 10-ft drop out of the last slide.<br/>&nbsp;</p><br>
